Class DomainNameContact

  • java.lang.Object
    • netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain.DomainNameContact

  • public class DomainNameContact
extends java.lang.Object
    An updatable contact object used within the Netistrar Domain Lifecycle API methods and as a related object to a DomainNameObject. Changes to key data for the owner contact for GTLD domain names require verification via email to the current owner for the domain name before these changes can be applied. If the change is accepted the domain name will be locked for 60 days for transfer.
